{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 964138, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 195417, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "没有这个服务", "timestamp": 1611334315, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 964175, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 195417, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "如果你愿意的话，可以自己找这个科目的一本不同的课本，重新自学一遍。或者就在今后的学习应用中去加深理解。", "timestamp": 1611334558, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 964180, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 195417, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "能及格的话，多多少少对这门课的基本原理还是有一些掌握的", "timestamp": 1611334593, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 964181, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 195417, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "或者，你就直接去找老师发邮件问，措辞一下，就说自己希望打好这门课程的基础。脾气好一点的教师会给你比较详细的建议。或者你就去加助教的微信，多多少少还是会给你建议的。", "timestamp": 1611334604, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 964183, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 195417, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "总而言之，要找“和这门课的教学有直接关系的人”去寻求建议，而不是到树洞来大海捞针。", "timestamp": 1611334627, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 964227, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 195417, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "谢谢Bob和Carol！我明天就去问", "timestamp": 1611334907, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 5, "pid": 195417, "reply": 6, "tag": null, "text": "对于考得差但是又没有挂科的科目，好希望得到一些后续学习建议啊...明明觉得自已学懂了，最后考得还是很差劲，究竟怎样才能达到教学的标准呢？", "timestamp": 1611334290, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1611334906, "url": "", "vote": {}}}